      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/32/10",
      "text": [
        " : \"أَهْدَى كِسْرَى لِلنَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ فَقَبِلَ مِنْهُ وَ أَهْدَى قَيْصَرُ لِلنَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ فَقَبِلَ مِنْهُ وَ أَهْدَتْ لَهُ اَلْمُلُوكُ فَقَبِلَ مِنْهُمْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4075 - Thuwair ibn Abi Fakhitah narrated from his father, from Imam Ali (as), who said:\n\"Kisra sent a gift to the Prophet (may Allah (swt) bless him and his family), and He (sw) accepted it.\nCaesar also sent a gift to the Prophet (may Allah (swt) bless him and his family), and He (sw) accepted it. Likewise, the kings sent gifts to Him (sw), and He (sw) accepted them.\""
        ]
      }
    },
